\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eLarge eggs\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eVanilla extract\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3BIgp4V\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003eFig jam\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSelf-rising flour\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eWalnuts\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3G0WSPH\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003eDried figs\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/figgy-pudding-christmas-pudding/?tp_image_id=102207\" data-pin-title=\"figgy pudding - Christmas pudding\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-figgy-pudding\"\u003eHow to make Figgy Pudding\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis figgy pudding recipe (or you could call it Christmas pudding, up to you) has three components:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eCake + Syrup + Cream = Christmas pudding\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEach of these is important to the final dish. The cake mixture is very easy to make—it’s just as simple as a muffin or \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/chocolate-baked-donuts/\"\u003ebaked donut \u003c/a\u003erecipe. The syrup is only three ingredients and takes less than 10 minutes to make on the stove, but it’s essential.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOnce the cake is baked in the oven, you must use a fork or toothpick to poke lots of small holes in the cake. Then, drizzle the syrup over it. The syrup will then ooze into these small holes you created, creating a moist and sort of bread pudding-type texture.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLast, you should serve this with whipped cream or even a scoop of vanilla (or egg nog) ice cream! This adds a creamy component that I think pairs well with the flavors and also just serves to make this dessert feel all the more special. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/figgy-pudding-christmas-pudding/?tp_image_id=102208\" data-pin-title=\"figgy pudding - Christmas pudding\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-batter.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-batter.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-batter-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-batter-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-batter-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeauti