156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/christmas-pudding-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/christmas-pudding-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/christmas-pudding.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-faq\"\u003eFAQ\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152942311\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is figgy pudding made of?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eThis recipe is a cake made with fig jam, dried figs, and walnuts. Then, a homemade glaze is drizzled over the top before serving. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152944117\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs figgy pudding the same as fruit cake?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eNo. Traditional figgy pudding is a British dish that is more like a bread pudding that may or may not include dried fruit like raisins. So although there are similarities for sure, they are not the same thing. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152945459\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDoes figgy pudding have meat in it?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eWhile this dessert version does not, traditional figgy pudding (like from 14th century England) probably did, which may have been mutton, beef, or even fish.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/figgy-pudding-christmas-pudding/?tp_image_id=102210\" data-pin-title=\"figgy pudding - Christmas pudding\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/figgy-pudding-recipe.jpg 1200w, https: